thread.title: Beth Mc Sorley
thread.title_full: Westminster Teak reviewed by Beth Mc Sorley

author: Beth Mc Sorley
title: Beth Mc Sorley
text: I appreciate Westminster Teak carrying the Golden Care product line for hardwood and teak maintenance. Because of the super pricing I was able to get 2 liters each of the Teak cleaner and the Teak protector for my four teak umbrellas. I have completed revamping one of my 9' market umbrellas. It is as if the umbrella is new again! I can't wait till all 4 umbrellas are done and it is summertime...I look forward to months of enjoying my investment in my umbrellas all because of this great line of products to protect my teak investment..I look forward to many years of summer shade in style by my beautiful pool. Thank you WESTMINSTER TEAK!!
